msgstr "Rubatsiro"

#: app/templates/help.html:7
msgid ""
"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Grylli inobatana nemirau yakavakwa mukati meapp kuti ikubatsire kugadzirisa "
"nekutonga kugadzikana kwako."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Iyi peji inopa pfupiso yezvakakosha uye zvinongedzo zvakananga kune "
"kwavanogona kutarisirwa."

