#: app/templates/account/manage_account.html:171
msgid ""
"Download all your account data as a JSON file. This includes your reminders,"
" messages, email settings, and more. The file is for your records only and "
"cannot be imported back. Protect it as it may contain sensitive information."
msgstr ""
"Dhavhanhura data rese raunorekodha seJSON file. Izvi zvinosanganisira "
"zviyeuchidzo zvako, mashoko, magadzirirwo emaemail, nezvimwewo. File iyi "
"ndeyemarekodhi ako chete uye haigone kuvakwa zvakare. Chengetedza sezvo "
